What is meteor?

Open source written using Node.js. All in one collection of libraries and packeages that all come together in this pretyy little frameowkr to amek web development easy. 

Why use it?
What used to take 1000+ lines of code can be achieved in a few hundred by combining 3 core features
1)Realtime designing
2)Database access using mongoDB 
3)No real latency

How?
Instructions on meteor.com
6 Different tutorials

Responsive design accross all platforms

Isomorphic javascript, Blaze, mongoDB, IronRouter
Not supported by all hosts

Free year of AWS!
